{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "浮云子在白云下院与石慧交手时突遭金弹丸暗器重创，崆峒众道人误认石慧、白非下手，知机子与玄天子相继出面追究。白非与邪异轻佻的玉鸢子交锋，察觉其掌法含迷情秘技；后那霞子现身，承认暗中发弹，并请求白非助她杀玉鸢子。白非、石慧跟随她旁观旧情怨，得知那霞子是青海齐齐堡主之女、苏敏君弟子，曾私授玉鸢子秘技而被负。那霞子终与玉鸢子旧情复燃，转而向白非交代海心山道路。白非、石慧赶往青海途中遇谢铿、丁善程，白非因谢铿断臂复仇之志而心生敬佩与矛盾。二人抵达青海湖边后遇红衫少女，白非凭香狸求见苏敏君，随少女乘皮筏前往海心山，石慧留岸等待。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_ji_zi",
      "speaker_name": "知机子",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"这位姑娘果然好功夫，神不知鬼不觉的就下了辣手，姑娘请稍等一等，我相信此刻敝教上上下下没有一个不想瞻仰姑娘风采的。\n\n\"",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他目光像刀一样的盯到石慧脸上，寒声说道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那我看倒未必吧。\"",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"慧妹快闪开。\"",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_ji_zi",
      "speaker_name": "知机子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"还好。\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_ji_zi",
      "speaker_name": "知机子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"嗯\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"看不出你功夫还蛮不错呢。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"此人在崆峒派中地位一定甚高。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那么今日之事，该是如何一个了局呢？\"",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhi_ji_zi",
      "speaker_name": "知机子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"二师弟的伤势如何？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_tian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄天子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这么狠毒的手法。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"好阔气的暗器。\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你姓万？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_tian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄天子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你从哲尔多来的？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这道士怪问些什么？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"黄金打造的暗器！\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_tian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄天子",
      "listener": "char_bai_fei",
      "text": "\"玄天子朗声道：\"",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"应该教训的是你。\"",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉鸢子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"好，好，好。\"",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_xuan_tian_zi",
      "text": "\"哪有师兄这样说师弟的？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"他望了白非和石慧一眼，又道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"突然面色一变，道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"小可为什么走不得呢？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_tian_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玄天子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你还想赖！\"",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"说话时，眼睛却在瞟着石慧，意思好像是在说：\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这暗器不是我打出来的。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"这个，你要问他才知道。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"手腕一抖，竟将背后斜插着的长剑撤了下来，\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他略为停顿了一下，望了望石慧，又笑了笑道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"我偏不要。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"是什么人？\"",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"嗖\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"飕\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"姑娘是……\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你是什么人，找我们干什么？\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"噢\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"怪不得她说帮过我们的忙。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "那霞子",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"玉鸢子——\"",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"你肯不肯帮我一个忙？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"什么事？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"玉鸢子？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"她是从青海来的——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"帮你的忙，也可以，不过——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "那霞子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"不过什么呢？\"",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "那霞子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你找她有什么事？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "那霞子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那是家师。\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"不是这意思——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_xia_zi",
      "speaker_name": "那霞子",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"妹子，你真好。\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我还没有答应，她却将我也算上了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你们男人坏死了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"喂\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你帮不帮我的忙？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"什么忙？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"我要杀死玉鸢子那坏蛋，你帮不帮我的忙？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我又没有说我不帮忙。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": "char_bai_fei",
      "text": "\"噗嗤\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"偏不让你知道。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我这算是什么呀？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我说他坏，就一定坏，难道你不相信我？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"她不等白非回答，又道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"她怎么又肯说了？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉鸢子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"情\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉鸢子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"蚀骨销魔倩女迷情大法\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 706
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"总有什么原因吧。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那姐姐会不会出事了？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"怎么只有一个人呢？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 746,
      "line_end": 746
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"玉鸢子。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 750,
      "line_end": 750
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这是怎么回事？\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 752
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你留在这里别动，我出去看看。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"道长过奖了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉鸢子",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"正是。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉鸢子",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"我和那姑娘之间本来有些小误会，现在已说开了，那姑娘不愿两位在此久候，因此特地叫贫道来通知一声，两位不妨到白云下院去歇歇——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 770
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"吁\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 774,
      "line_end": 774
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"那姐姐现在在哪里？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"小可倒还有些事，还是——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 786,
      "line_end": 786
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "speaker_name": "玉鸢子",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"不但那姑娘是例外，就连姑娘——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"还望两位能体谅贫道的苦衷。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你这厮又在玩什么花样？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 868,
      "line_end": 868
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_yu_yuan_zi",
      "text": "\"难道他说的话是真的？\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 894,
      "line_end": 894
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": "char_bai_fei",
      "text": "\"非哥哥，怎么了呀？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 932,
      "line_end": 932
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"那姑娘，你好吗？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 934,
      "line_end": 934
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"这是怎么回事？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 954,
      "line_end": 954
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"你看那姐姐和那个道士在一起，会不会快乐？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 972,
      "line_end": 972
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"风尘之苦\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 982,
      "line_end": 982
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"是呀！\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1012,
      "line_end": 1012
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"普通人若要赶路，在这种天气也不会像我们一样为了要抄近路，翻山而过——\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1012,
      "line_end": 1012
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我先赶上去看看好不好？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1024,
      "line_end": 1024
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他微微停顿了一下，目光询问的落在白非脸上，道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_shan_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "丁善程",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"他心中暗忖着，六合剑丁善程却向他身后一指，道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1070,
      "line_end": 1070
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"小弟惭愧，不能助谢大侠一臂，只有默祝谢大侠——\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1090,
      "line_end": 1090
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"但望了石慧一眼，他却不能不将这句话咽回腹中，改口道：\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1092,
      "line_end": 1092
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"义\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1120,
      "line_end": 1120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"道\"",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1120,
      "line_end": 1120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我就这样和他们一起睡吗？\"",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1148,
      "line_end": 1148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"那姐姐是我的好朋友。\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1213,
      "line_end": 1213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"慧妹真灵慧。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1215,
      "line_end": 1215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"这少女果然也是天妖的弟子。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1245,
      "line_end": 1245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shan_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "红衫少女",
      "listener": "char_bai_fei",
      "text": "\"那么你就跟我来好了。\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1253,
      "line_end": 1253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我们走了。\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1267,
      "line_end": 1267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "石慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "\"我们\"",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1269,
      "line_end": 1269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fei",
      "speaker_name": "白非",
      "listener": "char_shi_hui",
      "text": "\"慧妹，无论如何，今天晚上我也要赶回来，你——\"",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1271,
      "line_end": 1271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_shan_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "红衫少女",
      "listener": "char_bai_fei",
      "text": "\"喂，你走不走呀？\"",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 1273,
      "line_end": 1273
    }
